Student Management System

----------------------------------------
1. Project Description
----------------------------------------
This is a Java-based Student Management System.
It is used to manage student records like adding,
viewing, updating, and deleting student details.

----------------------------------------
2. Features
----------------------------------------
- Add Student
- View Students
- Update Student
- Delete Student

----------------------------------------
3. Technologies Used
----------------------------------------
- Java
- MySQL
- JDBC
- VS Code

----------------------------------------
4. Project Structure
----------------------------------------
- src/ (Java source code)
- database/ (SQL schema)
- config/ (database configuration)
- docs/ (project documentation)
- tests/ (test files)

----------------------------------------
5. Database Details
----------------------------------------
Database Name: student_db

Table: students
Columns:
- id (Primary Key)
- name
- email
- course

----------------------------------------
6. How to Run Project
----------------------------------------
1. Install MySQL and create database
2. Run schema.sql file
3. Update config.properties file
4. Run Main.java file

